'''Warra nuts''' were a green nut provided with [[Alcohol/Legends|alcoholic]] beverages at many bars on [[Coruscant/Legends|Coruscant]] and across [[The galaxy/Legends|the galaxy]], including the [[Kragget/Legends|Kragget]]. They had many different flavors, ranging from Hot 'n' spicy to salt 'n' sour.

==Notable aficionados==
*[[Darman Skirata|RC-1136]] a.k.a. [[Darman Skirata]] showed a liking for Warra nuts.
*[[Sev/Legends|Sev]] of [[Delta Squad/Legends|Delta Squad]] also has a liking for the nuts, and has been teased about getting gas from eating too many of the spiced variety by [[Scorch/Legends|Scorch]].

